Yes, someone can walk towards the door.
Well, what about it?
There's been a breakthrough.
While there were previously apps like Fitbit that could track activity, they didn’t give a reason to move like this game.
The charm of novelty disappears and use will fade in time.
However, because of Pokémon’s success, there will be other games that combine apps and virtual reality with real-world activity, helping many hunters to be more active, in better shape, and healthier.
